channel.title: Studio: Boosting Confidence :: Introduction to Web Dev
channel.description: At this point in your learning journey, it’s normal to have doubts about your progress. This class can be challenging. In this studio, we’re spending time as a group to discuss our experiences, as well as build our confidence in our coding abilities. Doubting progress is normal and common. Supreme court justice Sonia Sotomayor, Serena Williams, Tom Hanks, and multiple CEOs have all questioned their success. The struggle is real, and an open conversation often helps.
